Usage
================================================================================

List all map packages
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

::

   pyecharts-cli list


Install a map package
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

::

   pyecharts-cli install package-name


Uninstall a map package
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

::

   pyecharts-cli uninstall package-name

Show all installed packages
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

::

   pyecharts-cli freeze


Installation
================================================================================


You can install pyecharts-cli via pip:

.. code-block:: bash

    $ pip install pyecharts-cli


or clone it and install it:

.. code-block:: bash

    $ git clone https://github.com/pyecharts/pyecharts-cli.git
    $ cd pyecharts-cli
    $ python setup.py install
